            . I am a <rs id="t18290219-58-viclabel315" type="occupation">cheesemonger</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290219-58-victim575 t18290219-58-viclabel315"></join>. On the 20th of January I was standing in a passage between my shop and parlour, and saw the prisoner come in with two aprons on; he took off one, put a piece of bacon into it, and took it out - he went out of the shop, and dropped it in the street, when he saw me following him; I took him back.</p>
